{"type": "article", "id": 58198, "title": "一款防风保暖的骑行手套，手掌上有笑脸｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-11T22:57:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54135, "name": "Bent Hansen"}, {"id": 54136, "name": "Neff"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 44027, "name": "十二时慢"}, {"id": 54137, "name": "Reiko Kaneko"}, {"id": 54138, "name": "Jack Hudspith"}, {"id": 54139, "name": "Ben Pawle"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 200, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181111215021sncgq4Ox27BfXEeN.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Glove by Jack Hudspith &amp; Ben Pawle</h3><p>建筑师 Jack Hudspith 和产品设计师 Ben Pawle 联手创造了一个带有笑脸的骑车专用手套，以鼓励骑行者更好地相互沟通。每只手套的背面都是一面反光面，白天和晚上都能提高能见度，同时有一个带衬垫的笑脸遮住手掌。</p><p>设计师希望挥舞着带笑脸的手套将有助于解决一些经常出现在道路上的争执。这款名为 Glove 的产品以 Loffi 品牌推出，是两人在格拉斯哥艺术学院毕业后成立的新品牌。</p><p>这款骑行手套全年均可穿着，防水、防风、保暖、透气。手套的手掌处由双层聚酯纤维 AX 绒面革制成，有利于抓握，每个手指上都有触摸屏织物，佩戴者无需脱掉手套就可以在途中翻看手机。早鸟价 30 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/711642209/glove-for-happier-safer-cycling\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215113Cc3vnQ24q5EjIBo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215115etLMQgskBGpEdqzh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215116Wh1a2RVDTzM8LOjY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215116Ocrv0uTS8AfHqoad.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561587\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215117HD2aZ5gWsX0yCwP4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215118noKkN1JDFyAYgTEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215119gb4dOvA1QeWRoENh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>翩翩床 by 十二时慢</h3><p>独立家居设计品牌十二时慢推出新品翩翩床。设计师表示：“有梦的人如同鸟儿轻飞，自在洒脱。我们抛弃了笨重的床头柜，换成一双翅膀，用整合一体式的设计带给卧室更灵活的空间。摆脱哪些不必要的束缚，自由的在梦境中，翩翩起舞。”</p><p>这是一张有“翅膀”的床，左右翼自由选配，是床头柜，可以随意摆放物件也与床体合为一体，翩翩起舞。全实木的床板架，与床框以榫卯卡口连接。整床结构结实牢固，难以咯吱作响。中央另配一支中梁，形成六腿支撑，超越了一般实木床的承重力，最大承重达到了 600KG。</p><p>无论是一双翅膀上、床头板架上、床头板背后，都有地方安放你需要的物品，睡前读物、安眠香薰、夜灯或音响。床头的电线常常杂乱无章，设计师在床头板上下设置了贯通的线槽，让电线可以自由穿越，不用裸露在床上、交织在床边。售价 7900 元起，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c-s.w4002-15787199362.36.51f679d8hPOhuo&amp;id=581780550842\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215214fkSQWjHaIXmq28z9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215217DG1WElkefo3KysdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018111121521714CGXwPjEqAh2dRD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215218N6Bdq5Ze0JRA4fjn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112152183uhJ6txpEjCGAXFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>小绅士梳妆台 by 吱音</h3><p>关于梳妆台，这些你也许都遇见过。梳妆环境不够亮？心爱首饰要被“藏”起来？桌面化妆品堆积杂乱？原创家居设计品牌吱音推出了一款“小绅士梳妆台”，试图解决这些小尴尬。</p><p>梳妆镜自带发光灯带，USB 连接线，接通电源即可发光，均匀受光，照人更美，且可以灵活挪动和翻转。方便的立式收纳位，方便摆放。隔板可上下调节，梳妆台的顶部也可以有效的利用。双层抽屉收纳，桌面可灵活替换玻璃或者实木面，玻璃桌面时，就变身成一个美貌的首饰展台了。</p><p>台面下方还有隐藏的金属小挂钩。隐秘的暗格，预留走线孔，可以放入杂乱的插线板。售价 3599 元起，<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-b-s.w4011-16671124525.105.6f461abbxDkDcB&amp;id=581252622520&amp;rn=bf6ba2f4afeb774658540a6994ac66d2&amp;abbucket=11&amp;sku_properties=29112:97926\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215304kGqAf4Tyi9lED3NL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215305KTEA7qjim3dJzhbn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215306LsghYcUiGb74eNVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215306F9P4BXK18qQwYs3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215307SqvnxXD2AteBHLgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215307UMPZdLvbRX85uFlo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.277333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112153082fulOK8R1QXYstZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.485333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flavour-boosting Plate Collection by Reiko Kaneko for Neff </h3><p>英国设计师 Reiko Kaneko 的瓷器作品高雅又不失趣味。最近她尝试探索陶器的颜色、形状和质地，意在为陶瓷注入更丰富的体验。</p><p>这一系列限量版套装最近在米兰国际厨房展上亮相，包括一个前菜盘、一个主菜碗，和一个甜点碗，意在提升食客用餐每个阶段的体验感。</p><p>受到海洋启发，设计师用精美的骨瓷搭配蓝白玻璃，意在让人联想到鱼鳞的粗糙纹理。角形主菜碗由黑色粗陶制成，具有粗糙的砂纸状纹理，旨在增强辣味的感觉。例如，它可以提高泰国绿咖喱菜或是生姜的味道。基于覆盆子的形状，甜点碗旨在带出甜味菜肴的果味。粉红色增强了甜味的感觉，而外部圆润的覆盆子般的质地触发了与水果的联想。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215334gwvGTVP8x0mI4UlE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112153359GmLDjrgvOhY4N7o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215335J7Z0VnpaLr5gDb1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215336Q0TcVquUlYLb6weP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/11/10/neff-reiko-kaneko-flavour-boosting-plate-collection-gastrophysics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Primum Sofa and Lounge Chair by Bent Hansen</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 Bent Hansen 最近为其Primum 家具系列再添两款新品：Primum 沙发和 Primum 休闲椅。</p><p>这两件家具采用细长的底座、弧形扶手和柔软但极具支撑度的背部设计，采用纺织品牌 Kvadrat 的 Hallingdal 面料制成，赋予其经典和现代风格并蓄的外观。目前，Primum 系列已经包括一张餐椅，一张餐桌和两个酒吧凳，新品的加入，使得整个系列更加完整，用途也更加多元化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215419NwXid7mo3vKO1jCz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112154201IF7tMHhlDT09x3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181111215422s4AOFQtYWoXq6PE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112154224Vj0UNPFmeGcisdv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811112154232n0oZSc1KNCxze6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://benthansen.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bent Hansen</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}